Package: bamsignals
Type: Package
Title: Extract read count signals from bam files
Version: 0.99.0
Date: 2014-12-23
Authors@R: c(
	person(given="Alessandro",family="Mammana", email="mammana@molgen.mpg.de", role=c("aut", "cre", "cph")),
	person(given="Johannes",family="Helmuth", email="helmuth@molgen.mpg.de", role=c("aut", "cph")))
Author: Alessandro Mammana [aut, cre, cph], Johannes Helmuth [aut, cph]
Maintainer: Alessandro Mammana <mammana@molgen.mpg.de>
Description: This package allows to efficiently obtain count vectors from 
	indexed bam files. It counts the number of reads in given genomic ranges and
	it computes reads profiles and coverage profiles. It also handles paired-end 
	data.
License: file LICENSE
Imports: 
	methods,
	BiocGenerics,
	Rcpp (>= 0.10.6),
	IRanges,
	GenomicRanges
Suggests: 
	testthat (>= 0.9),
	Rsamtools,
	BiocStyle, 
	knitr,
	rmarkdown
LinkingTo: Rcpp, Rsamtools
biocViews: DataImport, Sequencing, Coverage, Alignment
VignetteBuilder: knitr
